container_info.post_install_tip: Click in the menu "Add-ons" -> "FinSheets" -> "Import" for setup and to import your data. A popup will open where you can connect to your Stripe & PayPal accounts. Open that popup every time you want to refresh your data.

name: FinSheets for Stripe & PayPal
description: Connect your Stripe and PayPal accounts and import and sync all your transactions data seamlessly for analysis
